{"tid":2277035,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★陳茂波：明年（2021）的人口普查仍需要招聘核查員、親身上門跟住戶進行面談訪問","createTime":"2020-11-08T07:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T10:14:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"589eaa8c2fe1dee1e6ed32f0f9b1b1af99e23761","tid":2277035,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"陳茂波又稱，新冠肺炎疫情的挑戰可能為相關的工作帶來不明朗因素，故此統計處將會進一步加強使用資訊科技以進行數據搜集的工作，例如讓普查員將收集到的數據即時輸入系統，又或提供已加密的網上問卷供市民填寫等。<br />\n<br />\n考慮到市民的不同需要，明年的人口普查仍需要招聘核查員、親身上門跟住戶進行面談訪問。統計處將會為所有前線的人口普查員提供適當的培訓和防護裝備，以保障他們及受訪住戶的健康和安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2797356/統計處明年中人口普查對政府政策有重要意義%E3%80%80陳茂波籲市民企業積極配合支持?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2797356%2F%E7%B5%B1%E8%A8%88%E8%99%95%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%99%AE%E6%9F%A5%E5%B0%8D%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%25E3%2580%2580%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E7%B1%B2%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq71I2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=c1719eb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2797356/統計處明年中人口普查對政府政策有重要意義%E3%80%80陳茂波籲市民企業積極配合支持?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"f6c7655dd2c28f5259afc44a8139fbdef15b0167","tid":2277035,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:43:42.000Z","msg":"人口普查群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fe445e3c456dc8f15dddb8991fd9d2ac3265d4","tid":2277035,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"水錶 電錶 都冇人抄，仲話家訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow